      "updated_at": "2021-02-16T23:11:04.431Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Hey y\u2019all, just want you to know that I solved this problem!<br>\nThe uZeus supports two ribbons, I had a second ribbon plugged into the uZeus with nothing else attached to said ribbon. I removed it, no more distortion.<br>\nDid I mention I\u2019m new to the whole video synthesis thing? I\u2019m new to the whole video synthesis thing.</p>",
